CalculateBusinessDays
=====================

Calculates the date for n business days from now, i.e. doesn't count Saturdays or Sundays. Will be adding ability to count business days in the past.


Example
=======
Say today is Fri, 28 Aug 2009

business_days_from_now(3)

returns

Wed, 02 Sep 2009

or you can specify a start date like this

business_days_from_now(7, Date.today + 3.days)

or

business_days_from_now(7, "Fri, 28 Aug 2009".to_date)

